.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, september, december, october, february, may, march
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, trike, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
14. the person driving the van is the person drinking water##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
| Birthday         | september    | october | april | february | march | may | december |
| Transport   | helicopter | taxi       | roller     | scooter | snowmobile   | trike    | van      |

