 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the french is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the american is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the mexican is the person watching action movies##1
10. the american is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the turkish##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is the italian##1
13. the indian is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
