 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the australian is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is the doctor##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person playing monopoly is the australian##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the person playing backgammon is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the colombian is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the person playing whist is the indian##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the australian##1
16. the person playing mah-jongg is the french##1

