10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the firefighter##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the mechanic is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the nurse##1
15. the person eating radish is on the left of the nurse##1

