 7. the person watching family movies is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
